                        "emailMessage/Body": "<p>The finding <strong> @{triggerOutputs()?['body/ovs_finding']}</strong> @{if(equals(variables('valueModified'), 'NCAT'), 'NCAT', 'RATE')} recommendation has been completed by <strong> @{outputs('Get_full_name_of_whoever_last_modified_the_finding_(inspector)')?['body/fullname']}</strong> and can now be reviewed.<br>\n<br>\n\n<a href=\"@{variables('findingURL')}\">Click here to review the finding</a><br>\n</p>\n\n---\n\n<p>La constatation @{if(equals(variables('valueModified'), 'NCAT'), 'de l’Outil d’évaluation de la non-conformité', 'RATE')}<strong> @{triggerOutputs()?['body/ovs_finding']}</strong> a été remplie par <strong> @{outputs('Get_full_name_of_whoever_last_modified_the_finding_(inspector)')?['body/fullname']}</strong> et maintenant disponible pour la révision.<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"@{variables('findingURL')}\">Cliquer ici pour évaluer la constatation </a><br>\n</p>",
